article_title: KPMG to Boost Health-Care Practice with Zanett Purchase
article_text:
KPMG LLP is buying Zanett Commercial Solutions, a Cincinnati-based technology-consulting firm that will help the Big Four accounting firm beef up the services it provides to health-care clients.

The deal was announced Monday. Financial terms aren't being disclosed.

Zanett has more than $50 million in annual revenue. The firm describes...
